name: Nipsey Hussle
description: Video of Rap Niggas. Nipsey Hussle was born on August 15, 1985 in Los Angeles, California, USA as Ermias Joseph Asghedom. He was an actor, known for Grand Theft Auto V (2013), Love Chronicles: Secrets Revealed (2010) and Caged Animal (2010). He died on March 31, 2019 in Los Angeles.
